        <abstract>
            <p>Offers to send some of his botanical field notes.</p> 
<p>Convinced that certain families and genera vary in certain directions. Cites <hi rend="italic">Lobelia</hi>’s "inclination" to produce albinos and other cases.</p> 
            <p>Reports a plant that is abundant in localities unfitted for its full development.</p>
            <p>Wild buffaloes will help a wounded calf.</p>
            <p>Response to CD’s views among American naturalists.</p>
        </abstract>
